ersion=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#FFFFFF\" background_enable_image=\"off\" background_size=\"custom\" background_image_width=\"20%\" background_position=\"bottom_left\" custom_margin=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding=\"26px|||||\" background_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" background_image_width_tablet=\"40%\" locked=\"off\" collapsed=\"on\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#F5F5F5\" custom_margin=\"||100px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||40px||false|false\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_enable_color=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost:10033/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/GOPR3539-scaled.jpg\" title_text=\"DCIM100GOPROGOPR3539.JPG\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"b327cbe4-b1d5-4b66-ad37-40c8f2f061ba\" header_2_font=\"Baskervville|700|||||||\" header_2_text_color=\"#005CC8\" header_2_font_size=\"48px\" header_2_line_height=\"1.35em\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_2_font_size_tablet=\"32px\" header_2_font_size_phone=\"20px\" header_2_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">COMBO LEVEL 1 &amp; 2</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Montserrat||||||||\" width=\"100%\" custom_padding=\"|0px||||\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our combined Level 1 and 2 package is the most effective pairing to learn and build the foundations of your freediving.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You will spend a full week immersed in the freediving life,<br />developing skills to become a condent 20-30m diver.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">On top of SSI Freediving Level 1 and 2, this package includes 2<br />coached training sessions (a savings of 90 USD) which can be used any time that suits your schedule and training needs  i.e. between courses or after completing Level 2.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Duration: 7 DAYS</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Check out the schedules of Level 1 and 2 for more information.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Prerequisite: 12 years old</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Pricing: $500 (IVA included)</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Including SSI Freediving Level 1 &amp; 2, and two coached training sessions</li>\n</ul>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Recreational\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"31b4f027-aaa0-4f2f-ae02-959764e19e4f\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"14px\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color=\"#48D1CC\" button_border_width=\"0px\" button_border_radius=\"100px\" button_font=\"Hind|700||on|||||\" custom_padding=\"18px|32px|18px|32px|true|true\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#F5F5F5\" custom_margin=\"||100px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||40px||false|false\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_enable_color=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost:10033/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/GOPR3565-scaled.jpg\" title_text=\"DCIM100GOPROGOPR3565.JPG\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"b327cbe4-b1d5-4b66-ad37-40c8f2f061ba\" header_2_font=\"Baskervville|700|||||||\" header_2_text_color=\"#005CC8\" header_2_font_size=\"48px\" header_2_line_height=\"1.35em\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_2_font_size_tablet=\"32px\" header_2_font_size_phone=\"20px\" header_2_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">ZERO TO HERO</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Montserrat||||||||\" width=\"100%\" custom_padding=\"|0px||||\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p style=\"text-align: left;\">After being introduced to our team and tted for your equipment, you will jump into SSI Freediving Levels 1 and 2, thus discovering freediving through the SSI system.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">After completing the courses, you will participate in the Master Program for 1 to 2 months, advancing all facets of your freediving knowledge: theory, dry practice, training<br />exercises, pool disciplines, and of course, open water training.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The more fully you integrate freediving training as a lifestyle in your daily life, the better diver you will become.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Together, we will decide when you are ready to move forward with SSI Freediving Level 3, SSIs highest level recreational course.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Duration: 3 months<br />(unlimited autonomous training and teaching internship after that)</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Prerequisite: 18 years old</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Pricing: 2400 USD</li>\n</ul>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Recreational\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"31b4f027-aaa0-4f2f-ae02-959764e19e4f\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"14px\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color=\"#48D1CC\" button_border_width=\"0px\" button_border_radius=\"100px\" button_font=\"Hind|700||on|||||\" custom_padding=\"18px|32px|18px|32px|true|true\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#F5F5F5\" custom_margin=\"||100px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||40px||false|false\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_enable_color=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost:10033/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/mysterious-ascent-scaled.jpg\" title_text=\"DCIM100GOPROGOPR3052.JPG\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"b327cbe4-b1d5-4b66-ad37-40c8f2f061ba\" header_2_font=\"Baskervville|700|||||||\" header_2_text_color=\"#005CC8\" header_2_font_size=\"48px\" header_2_line_height=\"1.35em\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_2_font_size_tablet=\"32px\" header_2_font_size_phone=\"20px\" header_2_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">MASTER PROGRAM</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Montserrat||||||||\" width=\"100%\" custom_padding=\"|0px||||\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Master program was designed to offer freedivers the opportunity to develop a fuller knowledge of their bodies aquatic capabilities in a semi-autonomous setting, under the guidance of an experienced instructor.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">This detail-oriented series of workshops and lectures is aimed at expounding upon the freediving knowledge and techniques that were introduced during the courses.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">After creating an initial training plan with our Instructor Trainer, your time will be split between theory sessions, coached training sessions (dry, pool and open water), autonomous training sessions, and free time in which<br />you will have the opportunity to explore the beautiful surroundings of the school, work on your stretching, and socialize with everyone at the school.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Duration: 1 month</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Prerequisite: SSI Freediving Level 2 or equivalent</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Pricing: 1000 USD</li>\n</ul>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Recreational\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"31b4f027-aaa0-4f2f-ae02-959764e19e4f\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"14px\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color=\"#48D1CC\" button_border_width=\"0px\" button_border_radius=\"100px\" button_font=\"Hind|700||on|||||\" custom_padding=\"18px|32px|18px|32px|true|true\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#000000\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_4,1_2,1_4\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost:10033/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/logo.ng_.png\" alt=\"logo\" title_text=\"logo\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_pres