in the freediving life,<br />developing skills to become a condent 20-30m diver.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">On top of SSI Freediving Level 1 and 2, this package includes 2<br />coached training sessions (a savings of 90 USD) which can be used any time that suits your schedule and training needs  i.e. between courses or after completing Level 2.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Duration: 7 DAYS</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Check out the schedules of Level 1 and 2 for more information.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Prerequisite: 12 years old</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Pricing: $500 (IVA included)</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Including SSI Freediving Level 1 &amp; 2, and two coached training sessions</li>\n</ul>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Recreational\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"31b4f027-aaa0-4f2f-ae02-959764e19e4f\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"14px\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color=\"#48D1CC\" button_border_width=\"0px\" button_border_radius=\"100px\" button_font=\"Hind|700||on|||||\" custom_padding=\"18px|32px|18px|32px|true|true\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#F5F5F5\" custom_margin=\"||100px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||40px||false|false\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_enable_color=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost:10033/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/GOPR3565-scaled.jpg\" title_text=\"DCIM100GOPROGOPR3565.JPG\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.19.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" 